Package: Rainmerging
Type: Package
Title: Merging functions for satellite and rain gauge time series  
Version: 1.0
Date: 2015-04-04
Author: Zed Zulkafli, Daniele Nerini, Bastian Manz
Maintainer: Zed Zulkafli <zedzulkafli.dev@gmail.com>
Description: Various non-parametric and geostatistical methods for combining 
    pixel (satellite, radar, etc) and point (rain gauge) precipitation. 
    Methods detailed in:
    Nerini, D, et al (2015) A comparative analysis of TRMM-rain gauge data 
    merging techniques at the daily time scale for distributed rainfall-runoff 
    modeling applications, Journal of Hydrometeorology
Depends:
    R (>= 3.1.3),
    zoo,
    gstat,
    automap,
    rgdal,
    sp,
    hydroGOF
License: GPL-3
